{"tid":2003136,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府記招：限制聚集人數是「一種精神」　無科學根據","createTime":"2020-05-05T14:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T15:19:28.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e138ce6f0a06b6c9078da3e317dc38289792e9b","tid":2003136,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/truthmediahk/posts/2950331601701008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftruthmediahk%2Fposts%2F2950331601701008&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRKmkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=1429ebe4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/truthmediahk/posts/2950331601701008</a><br />\n<br />\n【張竹君：限制聚集人數是「一種精神」 無科學根據】<br />\n<br />\n本港是日新增一宗武漢肺炎確診個案，該個案為輸入個案，即本港連續十五日沒有新增本地個案，總確診人數增至一千零四十宗。新增患者為一名二十七歲女子，由美國來港探親，上月十一日在美國期間曾經出現失去味覺、嗅覺、喉嚨痛和鼻塞等病徵，一星期後好轉，未有求醫。<br />\n<br />\n對於本港連續十五日沒有新增本地個案，衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君指本地傳播鏈有截斷跡象，形容現時「有少少安樂」，但重申即使過了兩個潛伏期，亦不能判定本地傳播鏈完全截斷，市民不應太快放鬆，亦應繼續佩戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n有消息指政府正計劃放寬限聚令，把聚集人數上限由四人增加至八人，被問到四人聚集與八人聚集在感染風險上之差別，張竹君指限聚令人數上限無實則科學根據，是「一種精神」，希望市民不要聚集，減低病毒傳播風險。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://wp.me/p5YkFQ-mtH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp5YkFQ-mtH&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRKmkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=db2fa1a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wp.me/p5YkFQ-mtH</a><br />\n<br />\n文、攝：Liona Li<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2LZTxMY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2LZTxMY.png&h=dbadc195&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cd10b111dbd099e6c93543eb4dc55954e8c1acd","tid":2003136,"uid":177552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:56:23.000Z","msg":"係宗教"},{"pid":"d28421e4c3f1f0d9853398df735d13a927c68122","tid":2003136,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港獨之父寄語港人：香港再出發＝抗爭再出發；並贈港人新歌曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2003117/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2003117/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n可惜，港獨之父冇咩音樂感，<br />\n原版實在太難聽，為免傷害聽力<br />\n<strong>有冇人可以幫港獨之父，重新填詞？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hSzXf1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhSzXf1F.jpg&h=583b4040&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fd9982cb7b8e34b605ee0d65ded2f4908a6993e","tid":2003136,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T15:19:28.000Z","msg":"所以咪一個都會犯限聚令囉<br />\n你精神上同隔離聚集就告得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}